==Divhazwakale==

Inwe ya khasho ya lushaka ye ya thoma nga 2 Luhuhi 1965.
Phalaphala FM yo bebwa nga murahu ha u tangana ha Radio Venda na Radio Thohoyandou.

Radio Venda yo vha I tshi sielisana tshifhinga tsha awara tharu tsha u hasha na Radio Tsonga, ine zwino ya vha MLFM.
Zwino ri hasha awara dza Fumbili Ina hu si na u ima.
I farwa Limpopo, zwinwe zwipida zwa Mavundu a Gauteng, Northwest na Mpumalanga.

Vhathetshelesi vha vhalelwa kha u fhira 1 000 000.
Tshifhinga tshine vhathetshelesi vha tshifhedza kha Phalaphala (TSL)  ndi 22hrs 48 minutes. 
 
